<br>
As Admin of this board for now what ? 9months or so? <br>
I have seen alot of Good and Bad of the Calendar.<br>
I originally started comeing to this board to fight for my Guilds (at the time Band of the black hand read archives page 12+)<br>
Right to be in the plane.<br>
<br>
I did this diplomaticaly and listened to others opinion and finally being asked to become an Admin to represent the smaller interests wich infact I still do (dont believe me ask my own guild /grin) <br>
<br>
I Frequently make choices, arguements or assist guilds to the Detrement or not in Direct benefit for my own guild.<br>
<br>
I try to remain as impartial as humanly possible.<br>
<br>
In this situation I can only see further rules being made.<br>
Currently there are 3 Guilds who rotate the God Cazic thule, With the Free days that are currently up and Available this allows those 3 guilds to kill CT with little or no trouble.<br>
If we lower the number in addition to what I will assume to be an increase of CR's this will also put the 3 current CT guilds and soon to be what I expect to be up to 6 guilds fighting/argueing/possibly running over smaller guilds to get to the end result, Or possibly another round of big brother type rules (Read page 5+ on guild rep forum)<br>
&lt;&lt;addin to this the Free days allow said CT guilds to arrange with guilds other days to do fear or do CT on the next day or some other compensatory action (SP) .&gt;&gt;<br>
<br>
All of wich will = more trouble on the Rathe as a whole.<br>
<br>
If we do choose to do a smaller number for plane Reservation I foresee new amendmants to make the &quot;uber&quot; happy so they arent running over the &quot;smaller&quot; or how ever you want to twist it.<br>
<br>
There are several reasons For and against the proposed change, I dont want anyone to be unhappy, and I like to have everyone to have fun in game.<br>
Problem being with any rule &quot;you cant make EVERYONE happy 100% of the time but you can make some of the people happy most of the time&quot;<br>
<br>
At this point the Vote is Very &quot;iffy&quot; for and against.<br>
<br>
I encourage all guilds who post to this forum to take all facts to account what is happening and what &quot;Could (tm)&quot; happen.<br>
<br>
Again I must Stress these are soley my View points as being an admin and not of any particular guild or association.<br>
